text: Saint-Paterne - Le Chevain is a commune. It is found in the Pays de la Loire region in the Sarthe department in the west of France. The municipality was created on 1 January 2017 and consists of the former communes of Saint-Paterne (the seat) and Le Chevain.Arrêté préfectoral 28 September 2016 == References == Category:2017 establishments in France Category:Communes in Sarthe
title: Saint-Paterne - Le Chevain
